        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This ruby-studded dawnsilver chalice can\u2019t be harmed by any substance it holds, no matter how caustic. Furthermore, liquid placed within the *Chalice of Ozem* never spills unless its carrier chooses to do so (using a single action with the concentrate trait).",
